## Identifying the Next Best Studies 

You can upload your data and the number of next studies you want to calculate in the web application below and get the design characteristics of the studies and corresponding A- and D-efficiency by sequentially adding these studies.

The data structure should be same as to the structure discussed in the earlier section and the input for the number of future studies should range between 1 and 15. Given the computational complexity of this analysis, the code will take some time to compile.

